            "creation_date": 1416287333,
            "body": "<p>Command + ; open Project Structure<\/p>\n\n<p>on left panel select SDKs<\/p>\n\n<p>in Sourcepath tab click +, select your src.zip<\/p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/XOUBc.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"><\/p>\n",
